---
title: Halloumi Veggie Jumble with Butternut Squash, Red Bell Peppers and Arugula
description: We can't say enough good things about halloumi cheese. This briny and squeaky cheese hails from the Mediterranean, and because of its high smoke point, it's great for grilling or pan-frying without creating a mess!
